## 6. Add Redis session service

```java
@Service
@RequiredArgsConstructor
@Slf4j
public class RedisSessionService {

    private static final String PREFIX = "session:";

    private final RedisTemplate<String, Object> redisTemplate;

    public void save(UserSession session) {
        String key = PREFIX + session.getSessionId();
        redisTemplate.opsForValue().set(key, session, Duration.ofHours(1));
        log.info("Saved session key={}", key);
    }

    public UserSession findBySessionId(String sessionId) {
        Object value = redisTemplate.opsForValue().get(PREFIX + sessionId);
        if (value == null) {
            return null;
        }
        return (value instanceof UserSession us)
                ? us
                : new ObjectMapper().convertValue(value, UserSession.class);
    }

    public void delete(String sessionId) {
        redisTemplate.delete(PREFIX + sessionId);
    }
}
```

